{"id":69001,"type":1,"name":"パーマン","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d2/d7/69001_wkCB6.jpg","rating":{"total":14,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":2,"6":1,"7":7,"8":2,"9":1,"10":1},"score":7.1},"summary":"飞人（作品原名：パーマン，Perman），此漫画是为藤子·F·不二雄的作品。\r\n\r\n故事讲述小学生須羽三夫（須羽満夫）在某天无意中“幸运地”遇上负责保卫银河的超人，被委以重任，成为保护地球的飞人1号。三夫原来只是一个普通的小学生，得到超人的道具后，包括力量头盔、飞行斗篷、PP呼叫器及替身木偶，成为拥有超能力的英雄。\r\n\r\n完结篇\r\n完结篇为主角三夫被选出到超人星学习，在临走前3号让他看了自己的真面目。在作者另一部漫画哆啦A梦中，已经成年成为明星的3号曾多次出现，坚守着青梅竹马的感情，仍然在等待1号归来。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>飞人</li><li><span>册数: </span>7</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/1523\">藤子・F・不二雄</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>超人小叮当</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>超人小天使</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>小超人帕门</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>替身飞人</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>哆啦A梦续集</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Paman</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Superkid</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Paaman</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Perman</li><li><span>出版社: </span>小学館</li><li><span>连载杂志: </span>小学館</li>","collection":{"wish":3,"collect":20,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"藤子・F・不二雄","count":9},{"name":"漫画","count":8},{"name":"子供向","count":3},{"name":"小学館","count":2},{"name":"童年","count":2},{"name":"科幻漫画","count":1},{"name":"星野堇","count":1},{"name":"儿童漫画","count":1},{"name":"恋爱","count":1},{"name":"日本漫画","count":1},{"name":"1967","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":1523,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5e/da/1523_prsn_fsFvc.jpg","name":"藤子·F·不二雄","desc":"作者"}],"relations":[{"id":53804,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/26/7a/53804_f7vhF.jpg","title":"パーマン","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/53804"},{"id":53755,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/8a/eb/53755_aSr8I.jpg","title":"パーマン","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/53755"}],"comic":[{"id":69004,"name":"パーマン (02)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover